      "rationale": "NIH predicted vs. measured at all 5 operating points: mean relative error 8.3%, max 12.1% (within combined experimental and model uncertainty). Pump head agreement within 5%. Relative hemolysis index RH computed for all geometric variants; worst-case RH = 0.87 < 1.0 acceptance threshold. Uncertainty bands overlap at all points confirming model adequacy.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/morrison/evidence/output-comparison-report-2023"
