      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry as the COU model. Operating conditions in validation span the full CPB clinical envelope. Blood analog fluid properties matched to clinical range. Validation hierarchy includes component-level (impeller channel) and system-level (full pump) activities, providing multi-scale confidence. Validation domain overlap with COU domain assessed as high.",
