      "rationale": "Iterative convergence achieved to residual tolerance 1e-6 for all transport equations. Mass imbalance < 0.01% at steady state. Double-precision arithmetic used throughout. Round-off error estimated negligible relative to discretization error. Solver settings (relaxation factors, linear solver tolerances) documented and version-controlled.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/morrison/evidence/solver-error-log-2023"
