      "rationale": "Simulation workflow executed under documented standard operating procedure (SOP-CFD-2023-04). Independent peer review of setup files, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts conducted by senior analyst not involved in primary analysis. Discrepancies identified in review resolved and documented. Checklist-based sign-off completed prior to results release.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/morrison/evidence/use-error-review-record-2023"
    },
    {
