      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes (RANS) with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on literature survey of rotary blood pump CFD. Non-Newtonian blood rheology modeled via Carreau-Yasuda model with published bovine blood parameters. Hemolysis damage accumulation via power-law (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) model. Model form uncertainty quantified by comparison with LES results from published literature (Bluestein et al.); NIH within 11% of LES reference.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/morrison/evidence/model-form-justification-2023"
