      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/model-inputs-mrl2",
      "rationale": "Geometric inputs derived from CMM-measured pump dimensions (tolerance ± 0.01 mm). Fluid properties (density, viscosity coefficients) sourced from peer-reviewed literature with uncertainty bounds. Rotational speed set to measured tachometer values ± 5 RPM. Inlet/outlet boundary conditions from pressure transducer measurements ± 1 mmHg. Input uncertainty propagated through UQ ensemble; Sobol indices identify impeller tip clearance and blood viscosity as dominant contributors (combined 73% of NIH variance).",
