      "rationale": "Dimensionless flow coefficient (Phi) and head coefficient (Psi) confirmed equivalent between validation experiments and COU operating envelope. Reynolds number range in validation (Re 12,000–38,000) fully encompasses COU range. Blood analog rheological parameters mapped to clinical hematocrit range via sensitivity analysis. Non-dimensional hemolysis index scaling verified against published pump similarity laws. Equivalency confirmed for all five COU operating points.",
